The sunflower field is connected to the daisy field. The poppy field is connected to the dahlia field. The dahlia field is connected to the lavender field. The lavender field is connected to the aster field. What is the shortest path from the lily field to the hyacinth field? Starting from the lily field, please list the flower names in order, including lily, separated by commas.
